AB  - The monthly market value statistics on outstanding United States Treasury debt are reported for the 1981–1984 period. In addition, a monthly series on privately held gross Federal debt is reported for the extended 1942–1984 period, together with monthly security-price indices for various Federal debt aggregates. Examination of the stochastic structure of T-bill prices indicates that the riskiness of T-bills has increased dramatically in recent years.
